name: SEXUAL PUZZLE
description:
SEXUAL PUZZLEThis is an old kind puzzle known to everyone as a spot. All the details of the puzzle are randomly generated, you have to move the details and arrange them in the right order, so that they will fit into the whole picture.In game
  • Beautiful art.
  • Levels of difficulty 3x3,4x4,5x5.
  • 12 Levels
  • Highscore table
  • Soft music
  • Achievements
